---

<section id="philosophy" class="py-32 sm:py-40 px-6 bg-neutral-50">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <h2 class="text-xs font-medium tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-neutral-400 text-center mb-20">
      What We Believe
    </h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="fade-in bg-white rounded-2xl p-10 border border-neutral-200 hover:border-neutral-900 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg">
        <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl text-neutral-900 mb-4">AI Changes Everything</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-500 leading-relaxed text-sm">
          AI doesn't just augment software development. It replaces the need for traditional teams, timelines, and capital structures entirely.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="fade-in bg-white rounded-2xl p-10 border border-neutral-200 hover:border-neutral-900 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg" style="transition-delay: 100ms;">
        <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl text-neutral-900 mb-4">Edge Over Cloud</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-500 leading-relaxed text-sm">
          The best businesses run where their users are. On their devices. In their hands. Not in a data center halfway across the world.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="fade-in bg-white rounded-2xl p-10 border border-neutral-200 hover:border-neutral-900 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg" style="transition-delay: 200ms;">
        <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl text-neutral-900 mb-4">Privacy Is Architecture</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-500 leading-relaxed text-sm">
          We don't add privacy as a feature. We architect businesses where user data never leaves the user. Sovereign by design.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
